enhanced_by.reason: targetAssetList provides a list of target assets, which is a prerequisite for targetAssetRoiList to function correctly.
allSourceAndTargetAssets provides a comprehensive list of assets, which can be used to verify the existence of the target asset before invoking targetAssetRoiList.
indexInfo provides detailed information about indices, which can be used to validate the ROI data returned by targetAssetRoiList.
userIndexPlans provides details on users' index-linked plans, which can be correlated with the ROI data to ensure consistency and accuracy.
